
							Apollo Nida had a surprising reaction to the news that he’ll have to pay more than $1M in restitution in his fraud case: Let’s party! The Real Housewives of Atlanta star was spotted at an Atlanta bash for co-star Peter Thomas and Cynthia Bailey’s Bar One on Thursday night, and only Radar has all the details of his unusual prison prep — and why wife Phaedra Parks was not by his side.
Nida posed for pictures on the red carpet at Thomas’ bash to celebrate his wife Bailey’s Ebony Magazine feature Thursday night in Atlanta. 
