“Bravo is getting some shooting done with them before Apollo goes to prison,” a Bravo insider confirmed to Radar. “They began shooting the new season and they will be filming some stuff with Apollo about the situation.”
But while Parks’ distance from Nida may seem concerning to some, the Bravo source insisted she’s standing by her man. “It sounds like she’s just trying to keep busy and that’s her way of staying strong,” the source said. 
